Counter_Name        :	TD_LDS_STALL_sum
Description         :	TD is stalled because it has run out of credits and it has data waiting to be sent out to the LDS. Perf_Windowing not supported for this counter. Sum over TD instances.
Expression          :	reduce(TD_LDS_STALL,sum)
SPM                 :	Not Supported
Dimensions          :	DIMENSION_INSTANCE[0:0]


Counter_Name        :	TD_NOFILTER_BUSY
Description         :	TD no_filter subblock is busy. This means the TD's no_filter pipeline (decode, format, data swizzle, data packing) could be processing non-sampler data. Perf_Windowing not supported for this counter.
Block               :	TD
SPM                 :	Not Supported
Dimensions          :	DIMENSION_INSTANCE[0:1] DIMENSION_WGP[0:4] DIMENSION_SHADER_ARRAY[0:1] DIMENSION_SHADER_ENGINE[0:1]


Counter_Name        :	TD_NOFILTER_BUSY_sum
Description         :	TD no_filter subblock is busy. This means the TD's no_filter pipeline (decode, format, data swizzle, data packing) could be processing non-sampler data. Perf_Windowing not supported for this counter. Sum over TD instances.
